<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="meantime-adv">meantime <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'miːntaɪm/    美 /'miːntaɪm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>其间；同时</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-meantime">in the meantime</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在此期间；与此同时：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The doctor will be here soon. In the meantime, try and relax.
医生很快就来。现在尽量放松一下吧。</p></div></div>